title: Keity Is Tired Of How Her Male Friends Treat Her
description:
Our Producer Keity loves how relaxed she can be around her guy friends. They treat her like one of the boys, but sometimes she thinks they forget she's a woman. And there's one incident that sent her over the edge. Did she overreact?
